{
  "id": "RAW_1cc2bd12",
  "title": "只有 0.9B 的 PaddleOCR-VL，却是现在最强的 OCR 模型。",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMzA5NjEyMA==&mid=2647675929&idx=1&sn=56d86173bb3454e1278f24607125b34f",
  "date": "2025-10-23 01:31:00",
  "author": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "siteName": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这几天，OCR这个词，绝对是整个AI圈最火的词。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">因为DeepSeek-OCR，甚至让OCR这个赛道文艺复兴，又给直接带火了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500192256\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4261744966442953\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1788\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=139c5079&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURqdxhtuavLyHy79vcxhVQose7LibibqmTODXSmGia1Z0z7r6kZOFqRljK4e4iaNAK9OmropZsPX2BAvFw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">整个Hugging Face的趋势版里，前4有3个OCR，甚至Qwen3-VL-8B也能干OCR的活，说一句全员OCR真的不过分。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后在我上一篇讲DeepSeek-OCR文章的评论区里，有很多朋友都在把DeepSeek-OCR跟</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">PaddleOCR-VL做对比，</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">也有很多人都在问，能不能再解读一下百度那个OCR模型（也就是</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">PaddleOCR-VL）</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500192249\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2712700369913687\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1622\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a6a748ba&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURqdxhtuavLyHy79vcxhVQosylGOcTyXUXyKVBWg0U1kxhqtFu6u0EeTQlQQsGcHYngUx796rv1j0w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500192252\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5829439252336449\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1712\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fd24f7ca&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURqdxhtuavLyHy79vcxhVQos9HuQyS1SbPHcA6iagUa4Hlu8tvzwBwUFQicmlpdBwWJJjtoZSUQ4IARQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以我也觉得，不如就来写一篇关于</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">PaddleOCR-VL的内容吧。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">非常坦诚的讲，百度家的东西，我写的一直都会非常谨慎。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是这个PaddleOCR-VL，是我真的觉得值得一写的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">因为，确实很牛逼。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500192273\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7833333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5b7000a4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURqdxhtuavLyHy79vcxhVQosJ9gQL0lqQbWzsGj2XR4d80a8ibT0reqjiaQQlibtvkj6mbYricB7OO8cmw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">首先提一下，PaddleOCR这个项目本身，不是啥新东西，这是百度一直都在做的项目，很多年了，最早期甚至可以追溯到2020年，也是一直是开源的姿态。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500192253\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5961995249406176\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"842\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2f212c35&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURqdxhtuavLyHy79vcxhVQosPERUE4H46icVnhQwOnaGKzDfRRN2YFicUSlhgV28evic7pfYmciaGhNenA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">后来他们就不断的迭代，整整5年时间，成了整个OCR领域最火的开源，现在也应该是现在Github上Star最高的OCR项目，有60K，基本属于断档领先。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500192254\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3315677966101695\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1888\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ec7b8a1a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURqdxhtuavLyHy79vcxhVQosicP3ub0rSjGWPWud2k7bZQOtsVlfX3h5ia1YKqVRyemAhMy02NjyQjXg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">PaddleOCR-VL模型，就是他们</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">前几天开源了他们的PaddleOCR系列里最新的模型，这也是第一次，把大模型用在了整个OCR文档解析的最核心的位置。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500192255\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5548266166822868\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2134\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fc0ea8bf&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURqdxhtuavLyHy79vcxhVQosugVUxVQeUAGTm12z3D65FgnCWJAhdtLDJYUv4qWkK3C6hkFNnaacLw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">整个模型只有0.9B，但是几乎在OCR的评测集叫OmniDocBench v1.5的所有子项，都做到了SOTA。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500192258\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5182049110922947\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1181\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=aa74cea7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURqdxhtuavLyHy79vcxhVQosFFTlHuvRKAFkiagf8ADIsAABiaibWpTiaoNDl5mO0G2NPD4c6LUK5mWdkw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">左边有三个类型，分别是传统的多阶段流水线系统、通用多模态大模型、专门为文档解析训练的视觉语言模型。</span></span></p>\n  <div>\n   <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">PaddleOCR-VL参数最小，效果最好，然后因为发的刚好早了三四天，所以表里没有DeepSeek-OCR的跑分，但是</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">OmniDocBench v1.5</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">的最新跑分昨天也出炉了，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">DeepSeek-OCR</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">综合跑分是86.46，比</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">PaddleOCR-VL的92.56还是低了大概6分，不过也能理解。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500192274\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.35555555555555557\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=960e1a8f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURqdxhtuavLyHy79vcxhVQos2YFlteSB1RmdibeHn4T4iaS1vWR2qcrZLwJAiaic64E3mW7Q0ddgSkqECQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">PaddleOCR-VL</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">确实足够的猛，在垂直模型领域，把性价比做到了极致。</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">你可能会有一点点好奇，为啥一个0.9B的模型，能比其他的大模型都要强。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">除了确实专精这个领域之外，还有个非常有趣的架构，是我觉得单独可以说一下的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">也是长上下文和避免幻觉的一种非常有趣的解法。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500192275\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4287037037037037\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=888aade1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURqdxhtuavLyHy79vcxhVQoscKzYAZ0cgCUIT7GYBUITlG6h5Xkfr9CHyuz0Xue1qEfhNm7Hf3WmLA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">很多的多模态大模型，是端到端的，他们干OCR的方式其实是非常低效的。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就是你把一整张A4纸扔给它，它需要一口气把这张图上所有的文字、表格、公式、图片、排版等等全都看懂，然后再一口气生成一个完美的Markdown，这个难度，其实也挺地狱级的。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">毕竟模型需要同时理解：“哦，这块是个表，它在页面的左上角，这个表有3行5列，哦表头是这个，哦内容是那个，它旁边的这段文字是在解释这个表……哦哎卧槽我第一个事是要干啥来着。。。”&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">PaddleOCR-VL的做法就挺高效好玩的，它的架构，就两步：</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">第一步，先让专干</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;1 1 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">布局分析的传统视觉模型上</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个玩意叫PP-DocLayoutV2，它干的活儿特纯粹，就是“框”。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">它以极快的速度扫一眼整张图，然后把一些区域都框起来，然后告诉你：“报告老板，这里是标题，那里是正文，这块是个表，那块是公式。” 而且</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">每个框的阅读顺序，也都是符合人类的阅读顺序的。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个活儿，在CV领域已经很成熟了，根本不需要一个大模型来搞。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500192276\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9385749385749386\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"814\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"542\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5d4337cc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURqdxhtuavLyHy79vcxhVQosbKEU48uXpKMzd939YsjSyu4L1ARBfr0DKEsotgFd1CSN3JtOpY5ZNg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">第二步，就是主力登场。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个主力，就是最核心的这个0.9B的PaddleOCR-VL模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">它现在接到的任务，根本不是去看那张复杂的A4纸。它接到的是一堆被</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;1 1 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">PP-DocLayoutV2</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">裁好的小图片。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一个任务是：“这是一张200x500的小图，我（</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;1 1 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">PP-DocLayoutV2）</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">已经告诉你这是个表了，你（</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;1 1 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">PaddleOCR-VL</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">）给我把它转成Markdown。”&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">下一个任务是：“这是一张50x50的小图，我知道这是个公式，你给我转成LaTeX。”</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后循环往复，最后，又准又快。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以这种做法，根本不需要复杂的几百B的大模型，直接上0.9B的模型，却能达到最完美的效果。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我之所以把这个点单独拿出来说，也是想表达我的一个观点：</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">在普通用户眼里，其实很多时候技术根本没有优劣，能解决用户的问题，就是最牛逼的技术。黑猫白猫，能抓到耗子的，就是好猫。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">至少我认为，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;1 1 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">PaddleOCR-VL的做法，就非常的巧劲。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我也专门找了几类特别有代表性，处理起来比较头疼的图片来给大家看一下实测的效果。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">首先肯定是扫描PDF，这种应该是重中之重，比如下面这张非常糊的扫描件截图，肉眼看起来也会有点吃力。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500192261\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6166666666666667\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1277\" data-height=\"788\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=dcdfbb6d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURqdxhtuavLyHy79vcxhVQosb7zk81yf6zv8sA3iaOPUfDKSW1rvwcoicsWUqxydAVFbsNs3XHjPKZzQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;Bk3wdNN92ozxRpxoR9WctjQcnSc&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;我先试了下扫描PDF，比如下面这张非常糊的扫描件截图。肉眼看起来也会有点吃力。&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0+13&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7402251362761162756&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:1}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;referenceRecordMap&quot;:{},&quot;extra&quot;:{&quot;channel&quot;:&quot;saas&quot;,&quot;isEqualBlockSelection&quot;:true,&quot;pasteRandomId&quot;:&quot;6eead959-8263-4471-b125-572a1d9f9ff6&quot;,&quot;mention_page_title&quot;:{},&quot;external_mention_url&quot;:{}},&quot;isKeepQuoteContainer&quot;:false,&quot;isFromCode&quot;:false,&quot;selection&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:19,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;selection&quot;:{&quot;start&quot;:0,&quot;end&quot;:39},&quot;recordId&quot;:&quot;GACOdlwvnowuFUxSMUBcYRhUnBf&quot;}],&quot;payloadMap&quot;:{},&quot;isCut&quot;:false}\" data-lark-record-format=\"docx/text\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">糊不拉几的，我眼睛看着都疼。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而把这个扔给</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">PaddleOCR-VL，它处理起来很顺利，先是把需要识别的地方框了出来，并打上了阅读循序的序号。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500192262\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7777777777777778\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1170\" data-height=\"910\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=084b99e4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURqdxhtuavLyHy79vcxhVQosDp6GtjIVqabgF602icyJSr71NE03sicfz5iaf90QzFm9c4QZbict99N2Gw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后是第二步，分块识别出结果，效果很不错，公式也识别出来了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;Bk3wdNN92ozxRpxoR9WctjQcnSc&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;然后是第二步，分块识别出结果，效果很不错，公式也识别出来了。&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0+u&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7402251362761162756&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:1}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;referenceRecordMap&quot;:{},&quot;extra&quot;:{&quot;channel&quot;:&quot;saas&quot;,&quot;isEqualBlockSelection&quot;:true,&quot;pasteRandomId&quot;:&quot;49d780f8-af2b-4c69-98af-5eee25e3468f&quot;,&quot;mention_page_title&quot;:{},&quot;external_mention_url&quot;:{}},&quot;isKeepQuoteContainer&quot;:false,&quot;isFromCode&quot;:false,&quot;selection&quot;